mathlete champion, Franklin Stubbs.

02:11.565 --> 02:14.566
In high school, I divided my time
between "The Wall Street Journal"

02:14.568 --> 02:16.435
and classic literature.

02:16.437 --> 02:19.838
By 16, I had a life plan
mapped out to my 65th birthday.

02:19.840 --> 02:22.141
