in the college infirmary,

02:24.511 --> 02:27.431
I had my heart stolen by a sympathetic
coed working on her nursing degree.

02:27.815 --> 02:30.349
Somehow, she found
my idiosyncrasies endearing.

02:31.285 --> 02:33.418
